{"tid":1347384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無警時份】經濟石鏡泉「藤條水喉通教仔」開口中 今回應：我係講自衞","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T06:18:35.000Z","uid":13353,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba799e0ea8a777c84e1588d818fe78c7d2f3713","tid":1347384,"uid":13353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》向石鏡泉問及當日「開口中」言論，他回覆指，「嗱，你睇返清楚，朱凱廸嘅Facebook話我嘅野，我係講，自衞你用藤條，即係唔可以用暴，噚日有人用（藤條），呢個係暴力，係任何人，無論黑、白衫都唔啱。」他說，「你係蘋果嘅，我唔知將會點寫，不過我講到呢一度，完了。」促記者翻看新界西立法會議員朱凱廸Facebook，記者詢問可否稍後回電，石鏡泉大喊5聲「講完」就收線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190722/59849508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849508&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=4b3b9163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849508&h=559c3e64\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190722/59849508</a>"},{"pid":"a72b997d2e7228c1eb7a455d556ad255e279c2a9","tid":1347384,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"屌你而家淆底"},{"pid":"6bad8413af27b62b9ac5126ddfe33feeee994e75","tid":1347384,"uid":13353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a72b997d2e7228c1eb7a455d556ad255e279c2a9","tid":1347384,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"屌你而家淆底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"6ef9d0e9febed2f13402106980bdbc907669553f","tid":1347384,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"即係有"},{"pid":"e0e1bdf3a3f0d637df37a173c826ce21a6164dd1","tid":1347384,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"冇仔送終學人教仔"}]}